720021f-a.title: Manhattan: Gold Street - Ann Street
720021f-a.text:
Gold Street, west side, north from and including Ann Street, seen across the clearing on the S.S. of Ann Street, and also showing B5-91 Ann Street, west of, adioining, and at the N.W. corner of
Gold Street.
July 28, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
